title: Katawa Shoujo for Android
description:
OK so here it is.

The final version of the KS port for android devices.

It is a full port of the PC version (with videos and all)

This is a (very good) visual novel,so don't expect too much gameplay.

I didn't made the port,if you want to thank someone or just stay tuned for news and bugfixes go here

Also please note that this is for +18

Instructions.

Copy both files to your android device.

Install the apk using any file manager.

Go to  /Android/obb/ and make a folder called vn.katawashoujo (if the folder is already there don't make another and skip this step)

Copy the file main.7.vn.katawashoujo into the folder that you just created.

Run the apk,don't worry if it takes time to load,it's normal.

If you have problems write a comment.

and please seed!
